column16: Andres Blanco lines out to right fielder Ezequiel Carrera.
Freddy Galvis flies out to left fielder Michael Saunders.
Odubel Herrera grounds into a force out, second baseman Devon Travis to shortstop Darwin Barney.   Cesar Hernandez scores.    Peter Bourjos out at 2nd.    Odubel Herrera to 1st.
Peter Bourjos singles on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Michael Saunders, deflected by shortstop Darwin Barney.   Cody Asche scores.    Cesar Hernandez to 3rd.
Cesar Hernandez doubles (6) on a line drive to right fielder Ezequiel Carrera.   Carlos Ruiz scores.    Cody Asche to 3rd.
Cody Asche walks.   Carlos Ruiz to 2nd.
